long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
You're looking at documentation but not the right version. The syntax is *probably* the same but you've been doing this long enough to know better, so you want the correct version.

This browser extension remembers which version of documentation you're using for PostgreSQL, Python,  Django, and Celery.

Request other documentation sites and more info at https://github.com/dougharris/unified_docs_switcher
